    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for that. i guess it depends on how much the increase is. i've heard a lot of people saying that raising the wage is just a way to force small shops to close while the big corporations take over since they can afford it. is there any actual evidence for that, or is it just more political talk?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
